simple Gradius arcade game developed for the course "Advanced Programming" at the University of Antwerp.

====GAME RULES====

* Hit upper or lower edge : lose 2 lives
* Hit planet or asteroid : lose 1 life
* Planets are indestructible by lasers. Explode at impact with player.
* Asteroids are destructable.

===SPELBESTURING===

* ESC : close game
* arrow-up : move up
* arrow-down : move down
* arrow-left : move left
* arrow-right : move right
* space : fire
